ygData.messageBody:
I have a friend who will power-level any
character you want up to level 20 in about a week. He
charges roughly $400 I think. There are some advantages
to this:<br><br>You get exactly the
name/race/class/server you want.<br>You don't have to worry about your
character's reputation.<br>You can still have the fun of
getting any items you want.<br><br>Of course, for $400
you could just buy a level 40ish character already
stacked with items. I'm just letting you know of this
possible alternative if you're interested.<br><br>Hope you
find what you're looking
for.<br><br>Nelmunbar<br>Enchanter on Brell
